      "content": "look i get the whole \"see a doctor\" thing but honestly i'm just looking for a straight answer. if i stop the zoloft today and start the st johns wort tomorrow morning instead, is that actually gonna cause a problem? or is it basically just a smoother transition because it's natural? i'm just trying to figure out if i can handle this switch myself since the side effects are so bad right now.",
